for
1 AN ACT relating to cities and towns; providing a tax credit
2 for expenditures to incentivize the improvement of
3 abandoned and nuisance properties; authorizing cities and
4 towns to designate abandoned and nuisance properties for
5 purposes of the tax credit; authorizing cities and towns to
6 assess a fee for costs to abate a nuisance or to repair,
7 remove or destroy dangerous property; and providing for an
8 effective date.
