4 (A) A property owner who improves
5 designated abandoned or nuisance property as provided in
6 W.S. 15-9-301 may apply for a property tax credit in the
7 amount approved by the governing body of the city or town
8 under W.S. 15-9-301(c) through (f). A property owner
